# The blog was rebranded to "The Journal". Permanently redirect old URLs
# so existing search rankings and inbound links follow to the new path.
# (Honoured by Netlify-style hosts; a client-side fallback also exists in App.jsx.)
/blog              /journal            301
/blog/*            /journal/:splat     301

# SPA fallback — let the client router handle everything else.
/*    /index.html    200
